name: Worldcoin from Ethereum
description: Bridged from Ethereum via https://bridge.pulsechain.com. Original Address - 0x163f8C2467924be0ae7B5347228CABF260318753. The Worldcoin system revolves around World ID, a privacy-preserving global identity network. World ID enables users to verify their humanness online (`Proof of Personhood`) while maintaining their privacy through zero-knowledge proofs.
